feed.description: This script synchronizes a SCAP collection with the 'Greenbone Community SCAP Feed'. The 'Greenbone Community SCAP Feed' is provided by 'Greenbone Networks GmbH'. Online information about this feed: 'https://community.greenbone.net/t/about-greenbone-community-feed-gcf/1224'.
